    "            </div>\n",
    "        </form>\n",
    "    </div>\n",
    "    <div class=\"border-top pt-3\">\n",
    "    </div>\n",
    "{% endblock content %}\n",
    "```\n",
    "{%endraw%}\n",
    "#### <code>form.hidden _tag()</code> works with the secret key to add protection against CSRF attacks.\n",
    "#### We need to create a <code>div class=”form-group”></code> for each of our variables.\n",
    "#### Username, email, and password will use the Bootstrap class <code>form-control-label</code> to create a text box for the user the type in the information.\n",
    "#### The submit variable will use <code>btn btn-outline-info</code> to create a button that the user can press to submit the form.\n",
    "{%raw%}\n",
    "#### When there is an error in the form, we will need the program to run a conditional. For example, if there is an error in the username, the condition <code>{% if form.username.errors %}</code> will be true. This will result in the error variable from the for loop to print.\n",
    "{%endraw%}\n",
    "#### Copy the following code into **<code><i>login.html</code></i>**:\n",
    "{%raw%}\n",
    "```\n",
    "{% extends \"layout.html\" %}\n",
    "{% block content %}\n",
