    "## Default Profile Picture\n",
    "\n",
    "### New users or users without a profile picture, will be automatically given a default profile picture.\n",
    "#### Since profile pictures will not alter the code as the application is running, the file we will create to save these pictures will be in the <code>static</code> folder. Name it <code>profile_pics</code>. Within this file, upload a default image. Make sure this image is named <code>default</code> as shown below:\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "├── webpage\n",
    "│   ├── static\n",
    "│   │   ├── main.css\n",
    "│   │   ├── profile_pics\n",
    "│   │   │   ├── default.jpg\n",
    "│   ├── templates\n",
    "│   │   ├── account.html\n",
    "│   │   ├── create_post.html\n",
    "│   │   ├── feed.html\n",
    "│   │   ├── layout.html\n",
    "│   │   ├── login.html\n",
    "│   │   ├── register.html\n",
    "│   ├── main\n",
    "│   │   ├── __init__.py\n",
    "│   │   ├── routes.py\n",
    "│   ├── posts\n",
