    "│   ├── __init__.py\n",
    "│   ├── models.py\n",
    "│   ├── site.db\n",
    "├── app.py\n",
    "├── requirements.txt\n",
    "```\n",
    "Type \"pip freeze\" into the terminal:\n",
    "> <i>(env) C:\\Users\\jenni\\OneDrive\\Desktop\\FlaskWebPage>pip install psycopg2</i> \n",
    "\n",
    "Copy all the requirements into the <code><i>requirements.txt</code></i> file.\n",
    "\n",
    "5. Now we have to tell Heroku what kind of app we are running. Create a new file called \"Procfile\".\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "├── webpage\n",
    "│   ├── static\n",
